{
  "page": "Fossoway twins",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Fossoway twins</b> were members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Their given names have not been revealed.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fossoway_twins&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_73_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">73&#160;AC</a>, the Fossoway twins entered the list in a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Old_Oak\" title=\"Tourney at Old Oak\">tourney at Old Oak</a> hosted by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakheart</a> in honor of the birth of a son. Both of them were defeated by a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> known as the \"Silver Fool\", which was later revealed to be Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fossoway_twins&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404115636\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.041 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1174/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 678/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1313/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansio